        		<a href="http://ah.189.cn/netup/web/broadzone/index.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://202.102.221.73/broad/files/image/all/ad/pro_pic.jpg" width="228" alt="不知道选哪个宽带好？点我帮你搞定"></a>
        	
